	<div class="entry-content">
		<p class="first-child "><span title="A" class="dropcap">A</span> while back I swapped my <a href="http://www.apple.com/macbook-pro/">MacBook Pro</a> for an <a href="http://www.apple.com/imac/">iMac</a> as my main computer. The iMac is a killer machine, but I was honestly a little frustrated at first.</p>
<p><a href="https://michaelhyatt.com/computer-productivity.html"><img src="https://michaelhyatt.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/iStock_87395693_MEDIUM-760x541.jpg" class="featured-image wp-post-image" alt="laptop" srcset="https://michaelhyatt.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/iStock_87395693_MEDIUM-760x541.jpg 760w, https://michaelhyatt.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/iStock_87395693_MEDIUM-300x214.jpg 300w, https://michaelhyatt.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/iStock_87395693_MEDIUM-768x547.jpg 768w, https://michaelhyatt.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/iStock_87395693_MEDIUM-575x409.jpg 575w, https://michaelhyatt.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/iStock_87395693_MEDIUM-460x328.jpg 460w, https://michaelhyatt.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/iStock_87395693_MEDIUM-518x369.jpg 518w, https://michaelhyatt.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/iStock_87395693_MEDIUM-82x58.jpg 82w, https://michaelhyatt.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/iStock_87395693_MEDIUM-600x427.jpg 600w, https://michaelhyatt.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/iStock_87395693_MEDIUM.jpg 1000w" sizes="(max-width: 760px) 100vw, 760px" height="541" width="760"></a></p>
<p>We all have ways we like to work. And some are more efficient than others. Over the years, I’ve tinkered and fine-tuned my approach for maximum productivity.</p>
